name: Austy OpenBeta
description:
Austy is a puzzel fps parkour building game.

there is 15 levels (so far)(only 3 in openbeta)

the game is a puzzel game where you have to parkour build to get to a green block. it sounds easy but its hard.

NOT OPEN BETA FEATURES:

when you have done the levels it will releas new world with more levels(no dlc)
